  <entry>
    <title></title>
    <link href="/2022/07/04/hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <url>/2022/07/04/hexo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs subunit">title: hexo搭建博客<br>date:2022<span class="hljs-string">-07</span><span class="hljs-string">-04</span> 12:58:50<br>categories:<br>- 博客搭建<br><span class="hljs-keyword">tags:</span><br>- hexo<br>- github<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="hexo和github搭建个人博客"><a href="#hexo和github搭建个人博客" class="headerlink" title="hexo和github搭建个人博客"></a>hexo和github搭建个人博客</h2><h3 id="1-安装node-js"><a href="#1-安装node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.安装node.js"></a>1.安装node.js</h3><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/liuqiyun/p/8133904.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/liuqiyun/p/8133904.html</a></p><p>检查安装是否成功：</p><ul><li>node -v</li><li>npm -v</li></ul><h3 id="2-安装git"><a href="#2-安装git" class="headerlink" title="2.安装git"></a>2.安装git</h3><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html</a></p><p>检查安装是否成功：</p><ul><li>git –version</li></ul><h3 id="3-下载Hexo"><a href="#3-下载Hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.下载Hexo"></a>3.下载Hexo</h3><p>安装命令：<code>npm install hexo-cli -g</code></p><p>检查安装是否成功：</p><ul><li>hexo -v</li></ul><h3 id="4-Github账号注册"><a href="#4-Github账号注册" class="headerlink" title="4.Github账号注册"></a>4.Github账号注册</h3><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv5107169/">https://www.bilibili.com/read/cv5107169/</a></p><h3 id="5-github仓库搭建"><a href="#5-github仓库搭建" class="headerlink" title="5.github仓库搭建"></a>5.github仓库搭建</h3><p>先点击+号，再点击new repository。</p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704091051023.png" alt="image-20220704091051023"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704091332166.png" alt="image-20220704091332166"></p><h3 id="6-生成ssh-Keys"><a href="#6-生成ssh-Keys" class="headerlink" title="6.生成ssh Keys"></a>6.生成ssh Keys</h3><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092148345.png" alt="image-20220704092148345"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092208181.png" alt="image-20220704092208181"></p><p>复制这个文件里面的东西</p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092309245.png" alt="image-20220704092309245"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092407057.png" alt="image-20220704092407057"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092436987.png" alt="image-20220704092436987"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092616545.png" alt="image-20220704092616545"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092632001.png" alt="image-20220704092632001"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092741538.png" alt="image-20220704092741538"></p><h3 id="7-本地生成博客内容"><a href="#7-本地生成博客内容" class="headerlink" title="7.本地生成博客内容"></a>7.本地生成博客内容</h3><p>新建文件夹用于存放博客</p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704092917470.png" alt="image-20220704092917470"></p><p>git bash here</p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704093108355.png" alt="image-20220704093108355"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704093309277.png" alt="image-20220704093309277"></p><h3 id="8-发布博客到互联网上"><a href="#8-发布博客到互联网上" class="headerlink" title="8.发布博客到互联网上"></a>8.发布博客到互联网上</h3><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704093802461.png" alt="image-20220704093802461"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094200336.png" alt="image-20220704094200336"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094218581.png" alt="image-20220704094218581"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094234029.png" alt="image-20220704094234029"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094252845.png" alt="image-20220704094252845"></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094306968.png" alt="image-20220704094306968"></p><p>生成界面东西全选就好，30天</p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704094411978.png" alt="image-20220704094411978"></p><h3 id="9-主题配置"><a href="#9-主题配置" class="headerlink" title="9.主题配置"></a>9.主题配置</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid</a></p><h3 id="10-配置分类和标签"><a href="#10-配置分类和标签" class="headerlink" title="10.配置分类和标签"></a>10.配置分类和标签</h3><p>输入以下命令：<code>hexo new page categories</code></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704125212155.png" alt="image-20220704125212155"></p><p>输入以下命令：<code>hexo new page tags</code></p><p><img src="D:/Typora/typora图片保存/image-20220704125340870.png" alt="image-20220704125340870"></p><h3 id="11-发布文章"><a href="#11-发布文章" class="headerlink" title="11.发布文章"></a>11.发布文章</h3><p>发布文章时，在文章开头加：</p><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs subunit">title: 这里是文章的标题<br>date: 这里是发表时间，如：2021<span class="hljs-string">-08</span><span class="hljs-string">-15</span> 08:15:16<br>description: 这里填写摘要。<br>categories:<br>- 分类<br>- 子分类<br>- 子子分类<br><span class="hljs-keyword">tags:</span><br>- 标签1<br>- 标签2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><code>hexo g</code></li><li><code>hexo s</code></li><li><code>hexo d</code></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
